msgid ""
"Responses to any customer satisfaction survey or details of any feedback,"
" complaints or requests for a review of our decision about whether you "
"qualify for legal aid."
msgstr ""
"Ymatebion i unrhyw arolwg boddhad cwsmer neu fanylion unrhyw adborth, "
"cwynion neu geisiadau am adolygiad o’n penderfyniad ynglŷn a’ch "
"cymhwyster am gyfer cymorth cyfreithiol."

msgid ""
"We will only save the information you enter if you decide to contact a "
"Civil Legal Advice operator. Therefore, the personal information that you"
" have submitted, will only be stored when you click ‘submit your "
"application’."
msgstr ""
"Cadwn ni ddim ond o’r gwybodaeth y rhoddwch chi os ydych chi’n penderfynu"
" i gysylltu â gweithredwr Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil. Felly, bydd y "
"wybodaeth bersonol yr ydych chi wedi cyflwyno ddim ond yn cael e chadw ar"
" ôl i chi glicio ‘danfon cais’."

msgid ""
"We know how important it is to protect customers’ privacy and to comply "
"with data protection laws. We will safeguard your personal data and will "
"only disclose it where it is lawful to do so, or with your consent."
msgstr ""
"Rydyn yn ystyried pa mor bwysig ydy hi i ddiogelu preifatrwydd cwsmeriaid"
" a chydymffurfio â chyfraith diogelu data. Byddwn ni’n gwarchod eich data"
" personol a dim ond ei ddatgelu lle mae’n gyfreithlon i’w wneud, neu "
"gyda’ch caniatâd."

msgid "Types of personal data we process"
msgstr "Mathau o ddata personol yr ydym yn prosesu"

msgid ""
"We only process personal data that is relevant for the services we are "
"providing to you. The personal data which you have provided will only be "
"used for the purposes set out below."
msgstr ""
"Rydym ond yn prosesu data personol sy’n berthnasol ar gyfer y "
"gwasanaethau yr ydym ni’n darparu i chi. Ddefnyddir y data personol yr "
"ydych chi wedi cyflwyno ar gyfer y dibenion isod yn unig."

msgid "Purpose of processing and the lawful basis for the process"
msgstr "Diben prosesu a sail gyfreithiol y proses"

msgid ""
"The purpose of the Legal Aid Agency collecting and processing the "
"personal data which you have provided in a legal aid application is for "
"the purposes of providing legal aid. Our lawful basis is ‘the performance"
" of a task carried out in the public interest or in the exercise of "
"official authority’ as set out in Article 6(1)(e) of UK GDPR. The tasks "
"are those set out in the Legal Aid, Sentencing and Punishment of "
"Offenders Act 2012. Specifically, we will use this personal data in the "
"following ways:"
msgstr ""
"Darparu cymorth cyfreithiol ydy diben yr Asiantaeth Cymorth Cyfreithiol "
"wrth gasglu a phrosesu’r data personol yr ydych chi wedi cyflwyno mewn "
"cais cymorth cyfreithiol. Ein sail gyfreithiol ydy ‘perfformio tasg a "
"chynhelir er budd y cyhoedd neu wrth arfer awdurdod swyddogol’ yn ôl "
"Erthygl 6(1)(e) GDPR y DU. Y tasgau ydy’r rhai a rhestrir yn Neddf "
"Gymorth Cyfreithiol, Dedfryd a Chosbi Troseddwyr 2012. Yn benodol, byddwn"
" yn defnyddio’r data personol hwn fel a ganlyn:"

msgid ""
"In deciding whether you qualify for legal aid. This is to assess whether "
"your issue is within the scope of the <abbr title=\"Civil Legal "
"Advice\">CLA</abbr> and whether you are financially eligible."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn penderfynu os ydych yn gymwys ar gyfer cymorth cyfreithiol. Hynny"
" yw, asesu os ydy’ch fater o fewn terfynau CCS ac os ydych chi’n gymwys "
"yn ariannol."

msgid "In assisting us in providing information and/or advice services to you."
msgstr "Er mwyn helpu ni darparu gwybodaeth a/neu gwasanaethau cyngor i chi."

msgid "To prevent or detect crime and fraud."
msgstr "Er mwyn atal neu ganfod trosedd neu dwyll."

msgid ""
"In conducting periodic assurance audits on legal aid files to ensure that"
" decisions have been made correctly and accurately."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn cynnal archwiliadau aswiriant ar ffeiliau cymorth cyfreithiol i "
"sicrhau bod penderfyniadau wedi eu gwneud yn gywir ac yn iawn."

msgid ""
"In producing statistics and information on our processes to enable us to "
"improve and monitor our processes to assist us in carrying out our "
"functions. This information is collated in an anonymous format, it will "
"not be used to identify you."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn cynhyrchu ystadegau a gwybodaeth ynglŷn â’n prosesau, yn ein "
"galluogi ni i wella a monitro prosesau er mwyn helpu cynnal ein "
"swyddogaethau. Coladir y wybodaeth hon mewn fformat dienw, ac ni "
"ddefnyddir y wybodaeth i’ch adnabod chi."

msgid ""
"Were the Legal Aid Agency unable to collect this personal information, we"
" would not be able to conduct the activities above, which would prevent "
"us from providing legal aid."
msgstr ""
"Ble na all yr Asiantaeth Cymorth Cyfreithiol casglu’r wybodaeth bersonol "
"hon, na allwn cynnal y gweithgareddau uchod, a byddai’n ein hatal ni rhag"
" ddarparu cymorth cyfreithiol."

msgid ""
"We collect ‘special categories of personal data’. This data is collected "
"where necessary for the purposes set out above. The condition under which"
" we process this data is Article 9(g) of UK GDPR – Reasons of substantial"
" public interest. Our associated Schedule 1 condition is Statutory and "
"Government purposes. We also collect this data for the purposes of "
"monitoring equality, this is a legal requirement for public authorities "
"under the Equality Act 2010. Special categories of personal data will be "
"treated with the strictest confidence and any information published under"
" the Equality Act will not identify you or anyone else associated with "
"your legal aid application."
msgstr ""
"Rydym ni’n casglu ‘categorïau arbennig o ddata personol’. Cesglid y data "
"hwn lle mae angen at y dibenion a ddatgenir uchod. Rydym ni’n prosesu’r "
"data hwn o dan amod Erthygl 9(g) GDPR y DU – Rhesymau o fudd sylweddol "
"i’r cyhoedd. Ein hamod cysylltiedig Atodlen 1 ydy Dibenion Statudol a "
"Llywodraethol. Rydyn ni hefyd yn casglu’r data hwn ar gyfer diben monitro"
" cydraddoldeb; mae hyn yn ofyniad cyfreithiol ar gyfer awdurdodau "
"cyhoeddus o dan Ddeddf Gydraddoldeb 2010. Ymdriniwn â chategorïau "
"arbennig o ddata personol gyda’r cyfrinachedd eithaf ac na fydd unrhyw "
"wybodaeth a gyflwynir o dan y Ddeddf Gydraddoldeb yn eich enwi chi neu "
"unrhyw berson arall sy’n gysylltiedig â’ch cais cymorth cyfreithiol."

msgid ""
"We collect ‘personal data relating to criminal convictions and offences "
"or related security measures’. This data is collected where relevant for "
"the purposes set out above. The Legal Aid Agency is an Executive Agency "
"of the <abbr>MoJ</abbr>, an Official Authority for the purposes of "
"Article 10 of UK GDPR."
msgstr ""
"Rydym yn casglu ‘data personol ynglŷn ag euogfarnau a throseddau neu "
"fesurau diogelwch cysylltiedig’. Cesglir y data hwn lle mae’n berthnasol "
"ar gyfer y dibenion a ddatgenir uchod. Mae’r Asiantaeth Cymorth "
"Cyfreithiol yn Asiantaeth Gweithredol y Weinyddiaeth Gyfiawnder, sef "
"Awdurdod Swyddogol ar gyfer dibenion Erthygl 10 GDPR y DU."

msgid "Who the information may be shared with"
msgstr "Gyda phwy y gellid rhannu’r gwybodaeth"

msgid ""
"We sometimes need to share the personal information we process with other"
" organisations. When this is necessary, we will comply with all aspects "
"of the relevant data protection laws. The organisations we may share your"
" personal information include:"
msgstr ""
"Weithiau mae angen i ni rannu'r wybodaeth bersonol rydyn ni’n ei phrosesu"
" gyda chyrff eraill. Pan fydd hyn yn angenrheidiol, byddwn ni’n "
"cydymffurfio â phob agwedd y deddfau diogelu data perthnasol. Mae’r cyrff"
" y gallwn ni rannu eich gwybodaeth bersonol gyda nhw yn cynnwys:"

msgid ""
"Public authorities such as: HM Courts and Tribunal Service "
"(<abbr>HMCTS</abbr>), HM Revenue and Customs (<abbr>HMRC</abbr>), "
"Department of Work and Pensions (<abbr>DWP</abbr>) and HM Land Registry;"
msgstr ""
"Awdurdodau cyhoeddus fel: Gwasanaeth Llysoedd a Thribiwnlysoedd EM "
"(GLlThEM), Cyllid a Thollau EM (CThEM), yr Adran Gwaith a Phensiynau "
"(AGPh) a Chofrestrfa Tir EM;"

msgid ""
"Non-public authorities such as: Credit reference agencies Equifax and "
"Transunion and our debt collection partners Advantis Credit Ltd;"
msgstr ""
"Awdurdodau nad ydynt yn gyhoeddus megis: Asiantaethau gwirio credyd "
"Equifax a Transunion a'n partneriaid casglu dyledion Advantis Credit Ltd;"

msgid "Hinduja Global Solutions UK Ltd and"
msgstr "Hinduja Global Solutions UK Cyf a"

msgid ""
"If false or inaccurate information is provided or fraud identified, the "
"Legal Aid Agency can lawfully share your personal information with fraud "
"prevention agencies to detect and to prevent fraud and money laundering."
msgstr ""
"Os darperir gwybodaeth ffug neu anghywir neu os canfyddir twyll, gall yr "
"Asiantaeth Cymorth Cyfreithiol rannu eich gwybodaeth bersonol yn "
"gyfreithlon gydag asiantaethau atal twyll i ddarganfod ac atal twyll a "
"gwyngalchu arian."

msgid ""
"Where a debt is owed to the Legal Aid Agency, we may share your data with"
" public authorities such as HMRC and DWP and with debt collection "
