"collection and enforcement."
msgstr ""
"Lle mae dyled tuag at yr Asiantaeth Cymorth Cyfreithiol, mae’n bosibl y "
"byddwn ni’n rhannu eich data gydag awdurdodau cyhoeddus fel CThEM a’r "
"AGPh a phartneriaid casglu dyledion fel Advantis Credit Ltd at ddibenion "
"olrhain, casglu dyledion a gorfodi."

msgid ""
"You can contact our Data Protection Officer for further information on "
"the organisations we may share your personal information with."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch chi gysylltu â’n Swyddog Diogelu Data i gael rhagor o wybodaeth "
"am y sefydliadau y gallwn ni rannu eich gwybodaeth bersonol gyda nhw."

msgid "Data processors"
msgstr "Prosesyddion data"

msgid ""
"We may contract with third party data processors to provide email, system"
" administration, document management and IT storage services. Any "
"personal data shared with a data processor for this purpose will be "
"governed by model contract clauses under data protection law."
msgstr ""
"Mae’n bosibl y byddwn ni’n contractio gyda phrosesyddion data trydydd "
"parti i ddarparu gwasanaethau e-bost, gweinyddu systemau, rheoli "
