"phrosesydd data at y diben hwn yn cael ei lywodraethu gan gymalau "
"contract enghreifftiol o dan gyfraith diogelu data."

msgid ""
"We contract with Advantis Credit Ltd as a data processor for the "
"collection and enforcement of criminal legal aid contributions. Any "
"personal data shared with the data processor for this purpose is governed"
" by model contract clauses under data protection law."
msgstr ""
"Rydym yn contractio â Advantis Credit Ltd fel prosesydd data ar gyfer casglu"
