"Cyfreithiol wedi gosod cyfnodau cadw ar gyfer y wybodaeth bersonol a "
"gasglwn, a gellir gael mynediad i hyn trwy ein gwefan ni:"

msgid ""
"You can also contact our Data Protection Officer for a copy of our "
"retention schedules."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch hefyd gysylltu â'n Swyddog Diogelu Data i gael copi o'n "
"hamserlenni cadw."

msgid ""
"While we retain your personal data, we will ensure that it is protected "
